            . I was in the service of Mr. William Hobson at Tottenham - I know these hay-forks - three of them are Mr. Hobson's, and one is my own; they were at the stack over-night.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. As I was coming from Tottenham I saw them lay near the five-mile stone.</p>
